  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK246">
<l>poruṇīṅkip poccāntā reṉpa raruṇīṅki</l>
<l>yallavai ceytoḻuku vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The wise) say that those who neglect kindness and practise cruelties, neglected virtue (in their former birth), and forgot (the sorrows which they must suffer.)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
